=== beginning_part_two ===

Tito watched helplessly as his beloved cat was carried away by the intrusive eagle. At first he fought back tears, but soon he realized how helpless he would be without the feline and worry left no room for sadness. He knew the birds were aware of these thoughts. He could only hope they would spare him long enough for Tito to fill the void left by his cat.

